  "sn18.2:1.1": "Linked Discourses 18 ",
  "sn18.2:2.1": "1 First Chapter ",
  "sn18.2:3.1": "2. Sights, etc.",
  "sn18.2:4.1": "At Sāvatthī. ",
  "sn18.2:4.2": "“What do you think, Rāhula? Are sights permanent or impermanent?”",
  "sn18.2:4.3": "“Impermanent, sir.” … ",
  "sn18.2:4.4": "“… sounds …",
  "sn18.2:4.5": "smells …",
  "sn18.2:4.6": "tastes …",
  "sn18.2:4.7": "touches …",
  "sn18.2:4.8": "Are phenomena permanent or impermanent?”",
  "sn18.2:4.9": "“Impermanent, sir.” …",
  "sn18.2:4.10": "“Seeing this, a learned noble disciple becomes disillusioned with sights, ",
  "sn18.2:4.11": "sounds,",
  "sn18.2:4.12": "smells,",
  "sn18.2:4.13": "tastes,",
  "sn18.2:4.14": "touches,",
  "sn18.2:4.15": "and phenomena.",
  "sn18.2:4.16": "Being disillusioned they become dispassionate. …”"
}